 <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"전체-코드-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%84%EC%B2%B4-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C-1\" aria-label=\"전체 코드 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>전체 코드</h3>\n<p>Flex item 레벨에서 약간의 CSS 코드를 추가하여 좀 더 다이나믹한 네이게이션이 되었습니다. 😁\n아래 Codepen 에디터 하단의 1x, 0.5x, 0.25x 버튼을 눌러보면 메뉴 아이템이 다르게 배치가 되는 것을 보실 수 있으실 겁니다.</p>\n<iframe height=\"590\" style=\"width: 100%;\" scrolling=\"no\" title=\"css-flexbox-navigation-2\" src=\"https://codepen.io/daleseo/embed/MWywwOj?height=590&theme-id=dark&default-tab=css,result\" frameborder=\"no\" loading=\"lazy\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\">\n  See the Pen <a href='https://codepen.io/daleseo/pen/MWywwOj'>css-flexbox-navigation-2</a> by Dale Seo\n  (<a href='https://codepen.io/daleseo'>@daleseo</a>) on <a href='https://codepen.io'>CodePen</a>.\n</iframe>\n<h2 id=\"마치면서\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A7%88%EC%B9%98%EB%A9%B4%EC%84%9C\" aria-label=\"마치면서 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 